{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The Value of Nothing: Out of Nothing Comes Something."},{"time":4000,"text":"That was an essay I wrote when I was 11 years old"},{"time":8000,"text":"and I got a B+. (Laughter)"},{"time":10000,"text":"What I'm going to talk about: nothing out of something, and how we create."},{"time":14000,"text":"And I'm gonna try and do that within"},{"time":16000,"text":"the 18-minute time span that we were told to stay within,"},{"time":21000,"text":"and to follow the TED commandments:"},{"time":23000,"text":"that is, actually, something that creates"},{"time":26000,"text":"a near-death experience,"},{"time":28000,"text":"but near-death is good for creativity."},{"time":30000,"text":"(Laughter) OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"So, I also want to explain,"},{"time":36000,"text":"because Dave Eggers said he was going to heckle me"},{"time":39000,"text":"if I said anything that was a lie, or not true to universal creativity."},{"time":44000,"text":"And I've done it this way for half the audience, who is scientific."},{"time":47000,"text":"When I say we, I don't mean you, necessarily;"},{"time":51000,"text":"I mean me, and my right brain, my left brain"},{"time":54000,"text":"and the one that's in between that is the censor"},{"time":56000,"text":"and tells me what I'm saying is wrong."},{"time":58000,"text":"And I'm going do that also by looking at"},{"time":61000,"text":"what I think is part of my creative process,"},{"time":64000,"text":"which includes a number of things that happened, actually --"},{"time":67000,"text":"the nothing started even earlier than the moment"},{"time":70000,"text":"in which I'm creating something new."},{"time":73000,"text":"And that includes nature, and nurture,"},{"time":78000,"text":"and what I refer to as nightmares."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81000,"text":"Now in the nature area, we look at whether or not"},{"time":85000,"text":"we are innately equipped with something, perhaps"},{"time":88000,"text":"in our brains, some abnormal chromosome"},{"time":91000,"text":"that causes this muse-like effect."},{"time":95000,"text":"And some people would say that we're born with it in some other means."},{"time":101000,"text":"And others, like my mother,"},{"time":103000,"text":"would say that I get my material from past lives."},{"time":109000,"text":"Some people would also say that creativity"},{"time":112000,"text":"may be a function of some other neurological quirk --"},{"time":117000,"text":"van Gogh syndrome -- that you have a little bit of, you know, psychosis, or depression."},{"time":122000,"text":"I do have to say, somebody -- I read recently"},{"time":125000,"text":"that van Gogh wasn't really necessarily psychotic,"},{"time":128000,"text":"that he might have had temporal lobe seizures,"},{"time":130000,"text":"and that might have caused his spurt of creativity, and I don't --"},{"time":134000,"text":"I suppose it does something in some part of your brain."},{"time":137000,"text":"And I will mention that I actually developed"},{"time":139000,"text":"temporal lobe seizures a number of years ago,"},{"time":143000,"text":"but it was during the time I was writing my last book,"},{"time":146000,"text":"and some people say that book is quite different."}]},{"cues":[{"time":150000,"text":"I think that part of it also begins with a sense of identity crisis:"},{"time":155000,"text":"you know, who am I, why am I this particular person,"},{"time":159000,"text":"why am I not black like everybody else?"},{"time":164000,"text":"And sometimes you're equipped with skills,"},{"time":166000,"text":"but they may not be the kind of skills that enable creativity."},{"time":170000,"text":"I used to draw. I thought I would be an artist."},{"time":173000,"text":"And I had a miniature poodle."},{"time":175000,"text":"And it wasn't bad, but it wasn't really creative."},{"time":177000,"text":"Because all I could really do was represent in a very one-on-one way."},{"time":182000,"text":"And I have a sense that I probably copied this from a book."},{"time":186000,"text":"And then, I also wasn't really shining in a certain area that I wanted to be,"},{"time":192000,"text":"and you know, you look at those scores, and it wasn't bad,"},{"time":196000,"text":"but it was not certainly predictive that I would one day make"},{"time":200000,"text":"my living out of the artful arrangement of words."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204000,"text":"Also, one of the principles of creativity is to have a little childhood trauma."},{"time":210000,"text":"And I had the usual kind that I think a lot of people had,"},{"time":214000,"text":"and that is that, you know, I had expectations placed on me."},{"time":218000,"text":"That figure right there, by the way,"},{"time":221000,"text":"figure right there was a toy given to me when I was but nine years old,"},{"time":226000,"text":"and it was to help me become a doctor from a very early age."},{"time":231000,"text":"I have some ones that were long lasting: from the age of five to 15,"},{"time":236000,"text":"this was supposed to be my side occupation,"},{"time":239000,"text":"and it led to a sense of failure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242000,"text":"But actually, there was something quite real in my life"},{"time":245000,"text":"that happened when I was about 14."},{"time":247000,"text":"And it was discovered that my brother, in 1967, and then my father,"},{"time":252000,"text":"six months later, had brain tumors."},{"time":254000,"text":"And my mother believed that something had gone wrong,"},{"time":259000,"text":"and she was gonna find out what it was, and she was gonna fix it."},{"time":262000,"text":"My father was a Baptist minister, and he believed in miracles,"},{"time":266000,"text":"and that God's will would take care of that."},{"time":269000,"text":"But, of course, they ended up dying, six months apart."},{"time":272000,"text":"And after that, my mother believed that it was fate, or curses"},{"time":276000,"text":"-- she went looking through all the reasons in the universe"},{"time":279000,"text":"why this would have happened."},{"time":281000,"text":"Everything except randomness. She did not believe in randomness."},{"time":286000,"text":"There was a reason for everything."},{"time":288000,"text":"And one of the reasons, she thought, was that her mother,"},{"time":290000,"text":"who had died when she was very young, was angry at her."},{"time":295000,"text":"And so, I had this notion of death all around me,"},{"time":298000,"text":"because my mother also believed that I would be next, and she would be next."},{"time":303000,"text":"And when you are faced with the prospect of death very soon,"},{"time":306000,"text":"you begin to think very much about everything."},{"time":311000,"text":"You become very creative, in a survival sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315000,"text":"And this, then, led to my big questions."},{"time":319000,"text":"And they're the same ones that I have today."},{"time":322000,"text":"And they are: why do things happen, and how do things happen?"},{"time":327000,"text":"And the one my mother asked: how do I make things happen?"},{"time":334000,"text":"It's a wonderful way to look at these questions, when you write a story."},{"time":339000,"text":"Because, after all, in that framework, between page one and 300,"},{"time":345000,"text":"you have to answer this question of why things happen, how things happen,"},{"time":349000,"text":"in what order they happen. What are the influences?"},{"time":352000,"text":"How do I, as the narrator, as the writer, also influence that?"},{"time":356000,"text":"And it's also one that, I think, many of our scientists have been asking."},{"time":360000,"text":"It's a kind of cosmology, and I have to develop a cosmology of my own universe,"},{"time":366000,"text":"as the creator of that universe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"And you see, there's a lot of back and forth"},{"time":372000,"text":"in trying to make that happen, trying to figure it out"},{"time":375000,"text":"-- years and years, oftentimes."},{"time":379000,"text":"So, when I look at creativity, I also think that it is this sense or this inability"},{"time":386000,"text":"to repress, my looking at associations in practically anything in life."},{"time":390000,"text":"And I got a lot of them during what's been going on"},{"time":394000,"text":"throughout this conference,"},{"time":397000,"text":"almost everything that's been going on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":399000,"text":"And so I'm going to use, as the metaphor, this association:"},{"time":403000,"text":"quantum mechanics, which I really don't understand,"},{"time":407000,"text":"but I'm still gonna use it as the process"},{"time":409000,"text":"for explaining how it is the metaphor."},{"time":413000,"text":"So, in quantum mechanics, of course, you have dark energy and dark matter."},{"time":420000,"text":"And it's the same thing in looking at these questions of how things happen."},{"time":424000,"text":"There's a lot of unknown, and you often don't know what it is except by its absence."},{"time":430000,"text":"But when you make those associations,"},{"time":432000,"text":"you want them to come together in a kind of synergy in the story,"},{"time":436000,"text":"and what you're finding is what matters. The meaning."},{"time":440000,"text":"And that's what I look for in my work, a personal meaning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444000,"text":"There is also the uncertainty principle, which is part of quantum mechanics,"},{"time":449000,"text":"as I understand it. (Laughter)"},{"time":451000,"text":"And this happens constantly in the writing."},{"time":455000,"text":"And there's the terrible and dreaded observer effect,"},{"time":458000,"text":"in which you're looking for something, and"},{"time":460000,"text":"you know, things are happening simultaneously,"},{"time":463000,"text":"and you're looking at it in a different way,"},{"time":465000,"text":"and you're trying to really look for the about-ness,"},{"time":469000,"text":"or what is this story about. And if you try too hard,"},{"time":473000,"text":"then you will only write the about."},{"time":476000,"text":"You won't discover anything."},{"time":479000,"text":"And what you were supposed to find,"},{"time":481000,"text":"what you hoped to find in some serendipitous way,"},{"time":484000,"text":"is no longer there."},{"time":487000,"text":"Now, I don't want to ignore"},{"time":489000,"text":"the other side of what happens in our universe,"},{"time":492000,"text":"like many of our scientists have."},{"time":495000,"text":"And so, I am going to just throw in string theory here,"},{"time":498000,"text":"and just say that creative people are multidimensional,"},{"time":501000,"text":"and there are 11 levels, I think, of anxiety."},{"time":505000,"text":"(Laughter) And they all operate at the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509000,"text":"There is also a big question of ambiguity."},{"time":512000,"text":"And I would link that to something called the cosmological constant."},{"time":518000,"text":"And you don't know what is operating, but something is operating there."},{"time":520000,"text":"And ambiguity, to me, is very uncomfortable"},{"time":524000,"text":"in my life, and I have it. Moral ambiguity."},{"time":527000,"text":"It is constantly there. And, just as an example,"},{"time":531000,"text":"this is one that recently came to me."},{"time":534000,"text":"It was something I read in an editorial by a woman"},{"time":536000,"text":"who was talking about the war in Iraq. And she said,"},{"time":540000,"text":"\"Save a man from drowning, you are responsible to him for life.\""},{"time":543000,"text":"A very famous Chinese saying, she said."},{"time":546000,"text":"And that means because we went into Iraq, we should stay there"},{"time":550000,"text":"until things were solved. You know, maybe even 100 years."},{"time":554000,"text":"So, there was another one that I came across,"},{"time":559000,"text":"and it's \"saving fish from drowning.\""},{"time":562000,"text":"And it's what Buddhist fishermen say,"},{"time":564000,"text":"because they're not supposed to kill anything."},{"time":567000,"text":"And they also have to make a living, and people need to be fed."},{"time":570000,"text":"So their way of rationalizing that is they are saving the fish from drowning,"},{"time":574000,"text":"and unfortunately, in the process the fish die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577000,"text":"Now, what's encapsulated in both these drowning metaphors"},{"time":582000,"text":"-- actually, one of them is my mother's interpretation,"},{"time":585000,"text":"and it is a famous Chinese saying, because she said it to me:"},{"time":588000,"text":"\"save a man from drowning, you are responsible to him for life.\""},{"time":591000,"text":"And it was a warning -- don't get involved in other people's business,"},{"time":595000,"text":"or you're going to get stuck."},{"time":597000,"text":"OK. I think if somebody really was drowning, she'd save them."},{"time":601000,"text":"But, both of these sayings -- saving a fish from drowning,"},{"time":605000,"text":"or saving a man from drowning -- to me they had to do with intentions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":609000,"text":"And all of us in life, when we see a situation, we have a response."},{"time":614000,"text":"And then we have intentions."},{"time":616000,"text":"There's an ambiguity of what that should be that we should do,"},{"time":621000,"text":"and then we do something."},{"time":623000,"text":"And the results of that may not match what our intentions had been."},{"time":626000,"text":"Maybe things go wrong. And so, after that, what are our responsibilities?"},{"time":631000,"text":"What are we supposed to do?"},{"time":633000,"text":"Do we stay in for life,"},{"time":635000,"text":"or do we do something else and justify and say, well, my intentions were good,"},{"time":640000,"text":"and therefore I cannot be held responsible for all of it?"},{"time":646000,"text":"That is the ambiguity in my life"},{"time":648000,"text":"that really disturbed me, and led me to write a book called"},{"time":652000,"text":"\"Saving Fish From Drowning.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":654000,"text":"I saw examples of that. Once I identified this question, it was all over the place."},{"time":661000,"text":"I got these hints everywhere."},{"time":663000,"text":"And then, in a way, I knew that they had always been there."},{"time":666000,"text":"And then writing, that's what happens. I get these hints, these clues,"},{"time":669000,"text":"and I realize that they've been obvious, and yet they have not been."},{"time":676000,"text":"And what I need, in effect, is a focus."},{"time":680000,"text":"And when I have the question, it is a focus."},{"time":682000,"text":"And all these things that seem to be flotsam and jetsam in life actually go through"},{"time":687000,"text":"that question, and what happens is those particular things become relevant."},{"time":692000,"text":"And it seems like it's happening all the time."},{"time":694000,"text":"You think there's a sort of coincidence going on, a serendipity,"},{"time":697000,"text":"in which you're getting all this help from the universe."},{"time":700000,"text":"And it may also be explained that now you have a focus."},{"time":703000,"text":"And you are noticing it more often."}]},{"cues":[{"time":707000,"text":"But you apply this."},{"time":710000,"text":"You begin to look at things having to do with your tensions."},{"time":713000,"text":"Your brother, who's fallen in trouble, do you take care of him?"},{"time":716000,"text":"Why or why not?"},{"time":718000,"text":"It may be something that is perhaps more serious"},{"time":722000,"text":"-- as I said, human rights in Burma."},{"time":725000,"text":"I was thinking that I shouldn't go because somebody said, if I did, it would show"},{"time":729000,"text":"that I approved of the military regime there."},{"time":732000,"text":"And then, after a while, I had to ask myself,"},{"time":735000,"text":"\"Why do we take on knowledge, why do we take on assumptions"},{"time":737000,"text":"that other people have given us?\""},{"time":740000,"text":"And it was the same thing that I felt when I was growing up,"},{"time":743000,"text":"and was hearing these rules of moral conduct from my father,"},{"time":748000,"text":"who was a Baptist minister."},{"time":750000,"text":"So I decided that I would go to Burma for my own intentions,"},{"time":755000,"text":"and still didn't know that if I went there,"},{"time":758000,"text":"what the result of that would be, if I wrote a book --"},{"time":761000,"text":"and I just would have to face that later, when the time came."}]},{"cues":[{"time":765000,"text":"We are all concerned with things that we see in the world that we are aware of."},{"time":770000,"text":"We come to this point and say, what do I as an individual do?"},{"time":775000,"text":"Not all of us can go to Africa, or work at hospitals,"},{"time":779000,"text":"so what do we do, if we have this moral response, this feeling?"},{"time":786000,"text":"Also, I think one of the biggest things we are all looking at,"},{"time":789000,"text":"and we talked about today, is genocide."},{"time":792000,"text":"This leads to this question."},{"time":795000,"text":"When I look at all these things that are morally ambiguous and uncomfortable,"},{"time":800000,"text":"and I consider what my intentions should be,"},{"time":802000,"text":"I realize it goes back to this identity question that I had when I was a child"},{"time":807000,"text":"-- and why am I here, and what is the meaning of my life,"},{"time":810000,"text":"and what is my place in the universe?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":812000,"text":"It seems so obvious, and yet it is not."},{"time":815000,"text":"We all hate moral ambiguity in some sense,"},{"time":820000,"text":"and yet it is also absolutely necessary."},{"time":824000,"text":"In writing a story, it is the place where I begin."},{"time":828000,"text":"Sometimes I get help from the universe, it seems."},{"time":832000,"text":"My mother would say it was the ghost of my grandmother from the very first book,"},{"time":835000,"text":"because it seemed I knew things I was not supposed to know."},{"time":838000,"text":"Instead of writing that the grandmother died accidentally,"},{"time":841000,"text":"from an overdose of opium, while having too much of a good time,"},{"time":844000,"text":"I actually put down in the story that the woman killed herself,"},{"time":849000,"text":"and that actually was the way it happened."},{"time":851000,"text":"And my mother decided that that information must have come from my grandmother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":856000,"text":"There are also things, quite uncanny,"},{"time":859000,"text":"which bring me information that will help me in the writing of the book."},{"time":863000,"text":"In this case, I was writing a story"},{"time":865000,"text":"that included some kind of detail, period of history, a certain location."},{"time":869000,"text":"And I needed to find something historically that would match that."},{"time":872000,"text":"And I took down this book, and I --"},{"time":874000,"text":"first page that I flipped it to was exactly the setting, and the time period,"},{"time":880000,"text":"and the kind of character I needed -- was the Taiping rebellion,"},{"time":883000,"text":"happening in the area near Guilin, outside of that,"},{"time":887000,"text":"and a character who thought he was the son of God."}]},{"cues":[{"time":890000,"text":"You wonder, are these things random chance?"},{"time":893000,"text":"Well, what is random? What is chance? What is luck?"},{"time":897000,"text":"What are things that you get from the universe that you can't really explain?"},{"time":901000,"text":"And that goes into the story, too."},{"time":903000,"text":"These are the things I constantly think about from day to day."},{"time":906000,"text":"Especially when good things happen,"},{"time":908000,"text":"and, in particular, when bad things happen."},{"time":912000,"text":"But I do think there's a kind of serendipity,"},{"time":914000,"text":"and I do want to know what those elements are,"},{"time":917000,"text":"so I can thank them, and also try to find them in my life."},{"time":922000,"text":"Because, again, I think that when I am aware of them, more of them happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":926000,"text":"Another chance encounter is when I went to a place"},{"time":930000,"text":"-- I just was with some friends, and we drove randomly to a different place,"},{"time":934000,"text":"and we ended up in this non-tourist location,"},{"time":938000,"text":"a beautiful village, pristine."},{"time":940000,"text":"And we walked three valleys beyond,"},{"time":942000,"text":"and the third valley, there was something quite mysterious and ominous,"},{"time":945000,"text":"a discomfort I felt. And then I knew that had to be [the] setting of my book."},{"time":951000,"text":"And in writing one of the scenes, it happened in that third valley."},{"time":954000,"text":"For some reason I wrote about cairns -- stacks of rocks -- that a man was building."},{"time":961000,"text":"And I didn't know exactly why I had it, but it was so vivid."},{"time":964000,"text":"I got stuck, and a friend, when she asked if I would go for a walk with her dogs,"},{"time":969000,"text":"that I said, sure. And about 45 minutes later,"},{"time":972000,"text":"walking along the beach, I came across this."},{"time":976000,"text":"And it was a man, a Chinese man,"},{"time":978000,"text":"and he was stacking these things, not with glue, not with anything."},{"time":981000,"text":"And I asked him, \"How is it possible to do this?\""},{"time":984000,"text":"And he said, \"Well, I guess with everything in life, there's a place of balance.\""},{"time":988000,"text":"And this was exactly the meaning of my story at that point."},{"time":993000,"text":"I had so many examples -- I have so many instances like this, when I'm writing a story,"},{"time":998000,"text":"and I cannot explain it."},{"time":1000000,"text":"Is it because I had the filter that I have such a strong coincidence"},{"time":1004000,"text":"in writing about these things?"},{"time":1007000,"text":"Or is it a kind of serendipity that we cannot explain, like the cosmological constant?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014000,"text":"A big thing that I also think about is accidents."},{"time":1017000,"text":"And as I said, my mother did not believe in randomness."},{"time":1020000,"text":"What is the nature of accidents?"},{"time":1022000,"text":"And how are we going to assign what the responsibility and the causes are,"},{"time":1026000,"text":"outside of a court of law?"},{"time":1029000,"text":"I was able to see that in a firsthand way,"},{"time":1032000,"text":"when I went to beautiful Dong village, in Guizhou, the poorest province of China."},{"time":1038000,"text":"And I saw this beautiful place. I knew I wanted to come back."},{"time":1040000,"text":"And I had a chance to do that, when National Geographic asked me"},{"time":1043000,"text":"if I wanted to write anything about China."},{"time":1045000,"text":"And I said yes, about this village of singing people, singing minority."},{"time":1050000,"text":"And they agreed, and between the time I saw this place and the next time I went,"},{"time":1055000,"text":"there was a terrible accident. A man, an old man, fell asleep,"},{"time":1059000,"text":"and his quilt dropped in a pan of fire that kept him warm."},{"time":1062000,"text":"60 homes were destroyed, and 40 were damaged."},{"time":1068000,"text":"Responsibility was assigned to the family."},{"time":1070000,"text":"The man's sons were banished to live three kilometers away, in a cowshed."},{"time":1074000,"text":"And, of course, as Westerners, we say, \"Well, it was an accident. That's not fair."},{"time":1078000,"text":"It's the son, not the father.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1080000,"text":"When I go on a story, I have to let go of those kinds of beliefs."},{"time":1086000,"text":"It takes a while, but I have to let go of them and just go there, and be there."},{"time":1090000,"text":"And so I was there on three occasions, different seasons."},{"time":1093000,"text":"And I began to sense something different about the history,"},{"time":1097000,"text":"and what had happened before, and the nature of life in a very poor village,"},{"time":1101000,"text":"and what you find as your joys, and your rituals, your traditions, your links"},{"time":1104000,"text":"with other families. And I saw how this had a kind of justice, in its responsibility."},{"time":1114000,"text":"I was able to find out also about the ceremony that they were using,"},{"time":1119000,"text":"a ceremony they hadn't used in about 29 years. And it was to send some men"},{"time":1127000,"text":"-- a Feng Shui master sent men down to the underworld on ghost horses."},{"time":1131000,"text":"Now you, as Westerners, and I, as Westerners,"},{"time":1134000,"text":"would say well, that's superstition. But after being there for a while,"},{"time":1137000,"text":"and seeing the amazing things that happened,"},{"time":1140000,"text":"you begin to wonder whose beliefs are those that are in operation in the world,"},{"time":1145000,"text":"determining how things happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1148000,"text":"So I remained with them, and the more I wrote that story,"},{"time":1151000,"text":"the more I got into those beliefs, and I think that's important for me"},{"time":1155000,"text":"-- to take on the beliefs, because that is where the story is real,"},{"time":1158000,"text":"and that is where I'm gonna find the answers"},{"time":1160000,"text":"to how I feel about certain questions that I have in life."},{"time":1165000,"text":"Years go by, of course, and the writing, it doesn't happen instantly,"},{"time":1168000,"text":"as I'm trying to convey it to you here at TED."},{"time":1172000,"text":"The book comes and it goes. When it arrives, it is no longer my book."},{"time":1177000,"text":"It is in the hands of readers, and they interpret it differently."},{"time":1181000,"text":"But I go back to this question of, how do I create something out of nothing?"},{"time":1187000,"text":"And how do I create my own life?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1190000,"text":"And I think it is by questioning,"},{"time":1192000,"text":"and saying to myself that there are no absolute truths."},{"time":1197000,"text":"I believe in specifics, the specifics of story,"},{"time":1201000,"text":"and the past, the specifics of that past,"},{"time":1204000,"text":"and what is happening in the story at that point."},{"time":1208000,"text":"I also believe that in thinking about things --"},{"time":1211000,"text":"my thinking about luck, and fate, and coincidences and accidents,"},{"time":1215000,"text":"God's will, and the synchrony of mysterious forces --"},{"time":1219000,"text":"I will come to some notion of what that is, how we create."},{"time":1225000,"text":"I have to think of my role. Where I am in the universe,"},{"time":1229000,"text":"and did somebody intend for me to be that way, or is it just something I came up with?"},{"time":1234000,"text":"And I also can find that by imagining fully, and becoming what is imagined --"},{"time":1242000,"text":"and yet is in that real world, the fictional world."},{"time":1245000,"text":"And that is how I find particles of truth, not the absolute truth, or the whole truth."},{"time":1253000,"text":"And they have to be in all possibilities,"},{"time":1255000,"text":"including those I never considered before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1258000,"text":"So, there are never complete answers."},{"time":1261000,"text":"Or rather, if there is an answer, it is to remind"},{"time":1266000,"text":"myself that there is uncertainty in everything,"},{"time":1270000,"text":"and that is good, because then I will discover something new."},{"time":1275000,"text":"And if there is a partial answer, a more complete answer from me,"},{"time":1279000,"text":"it is to simply imagine."},{"time":1282000,"text":"And to imagine is to put myself in that story,"},{"time":1286000,"text":"until there was only -- there is a transparency between me and the story that I am creating."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1292000,"text":"And that's how I've discovered that if I feel what is in the story"},{"time":1298000,"text":"-- in one story -- then I come the closest, I think,"},{"time":1304000,"text":"to knowing what compassion is, to feeling that compassion."},{"time":1308000,"text":"Because for everything,"},{"time":1310000,"text":"in that question of how things happen, it has to do with the feeling."},{"time":1314000,"text":"I have to become the story in order to understand a lot of that."},{"time":1320000,"text":"We've come to the end of the talk,"},{"time":1322000,"text":"and I will reveal what is in the bag, and it is the muse,"},{"time":1326000,"text":"and it is the things that transform in our lives,"},{"time":1329000,"text":"that are wonderful and stay with us."},{"time":1339000,"text":"There she is."},{"time":1340000,"text":"Thank you very much!"},{"time":1342000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}